 also start the game and dim the light.\n\n3) Press B on the right controller to turn on your flashlight. Use it to kill the enemies that are now spawning faster and faster and coming to find you. Just hold the light on them for 5 seconds.\n\n4) If the enemies get too close you will loose health and the game will stop and show your score. Restart with A on the right controller.", "short_description": "Oculus Passthrough has Zombies in your Livingroom! Kill them with your flashlight before they get you!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/zombiesprivacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Cazforshort", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/zombiesprivacypolicy", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["HORROR", "SHOOTER", "ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "5370311139648746"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "5220913331287331"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "5220913331287331"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1647025500, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "5220913331287331"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "4276468232452870", "version": "0.2"}, "id": "4796007810439091", "channel_name": "LIVE